                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-neutral-200">
          <p class="text-sm text-center text-neutral-600">&copy; 2025 Baehub. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
